    {
      "id": "home-hero",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Twilite",
      "position": {
        "x": -40,
        "y": -640
      },
      "width": 860,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# The graph is the product.\n\n**Twilite** is a **graph-native workspace** where visual thinking meets AI collaboration — treating graphs as **durable, portable artifacts** that humans and agents can both read and write.\n\n**One-liner:**\n> *“Figma meets ChatGPT for visual thinking.”* Describe what you want → an AI generates a graph → paste it into Twilite → it appears instantly.\n\n**Start:**\n- Full app: `/browser/`\n- Editor-only: `/editor/`\n\n**Follow the build:** `mailto:admin@twilite.zone?subject=Twilite%20%E2%80%94%20early%20access`",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "/",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
