    {
      "id": "home-thesis",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Core insight",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": -220
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Core insight\n\nMost tools treat graphs as UI state.\n\nTwilite treats the graph as the artifact.",
