    {
      "id": "problem",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The problem",
      "position": {
        "x": 740,
        "y": 60
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The problem\n\n- ❌ Graphs are ephemeral — screenshots, not files\n- ❌ No stable identity — no diff, no review, no versioning\n- ❌ AI can’t help — formats aren’t machine-writable\n- ❌ Rebuild from scratch — no templates, no remix culture",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
