    {
      "id": "how",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "How it works",
      "position": {
        "x": -40,
        "y": 470
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## How it works\n\nTwilite makes the graph a first-class artifact and gives AI a safe mutation contract.\n\n1. **Describe** what you want (to an AI or a teammate)\n2. **Generate** graph JSON (or deltas) with stable IDs\n3. **Paste** into Twilite → it renders instantly\n4. **Evolve** it tomorrow without losing coherence",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
