    {
      "id": "artifact-shape",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Artifact shape",
      "position": {
        "x": 560,
        "y": 470
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Artifact shape\n\nPortable JSON. Stable IDs. Open in Git. Review in PRs.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"fileVersion\": \"1.0\",\n  \"metadata\": { /* ... */ },\n  \"viewport\": { /* ... */ },\n  \"nodes\": [ /* ... */ ],\n  \"edges\": [ /* ... */ ],\n  \"clusters\": [ /* ... */ ]\n}\n```",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
