      "id": "mutation-contract",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "AI mutation contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -40,
        "y": 900
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## AI mutation contract\n\nDeltas over rewrites. Validation gates. Minimal payloads. Dry-run previews.\n\nThe goal is predictable evolution, not chaos.\n\n```text\ncreate  → add nodes/edges\nupdate  → modify existing by ID\ndelete  → remove by ID\nbatch   → apply multiple operations\n```",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
